  - id: FEATURES
    speaker: Ally Quinn
    line: Let me show you what this system can do. Click to continue...
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: 
    nextId: TYPEWRITER
    choices: []
  - id: TYPEWRITER
    speaker: Ally Quinn
    line: Notice the typewriter effect? The text appears character by character.
      Pretty cool, right?
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    emotion: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: 
    nextId: CHOICES_INTRO
    choices: []
  - id: CHOICES_INTRO
    speaker: Ally Quinn
    line: Now let's try something interactive. What would you like to see?
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: 
    nextId: 
