      requiresFlag: 
    - text: Show me branching dialogue
      nextId: BRANCHING
      requiresFlag: 
    - text: I'm ready to finish
      nextId: FINISH
      requiresFlag: 
  - id: PORTRAITS
    speaker: Ally Quinn
    line: The system supports character portraits with different emotions. When you
      add portrait sprites, they'll show up here on the left!
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    emotion: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: 
    nextId: BACK_TO_MENU
    choices: []
  - id: BRANCHING
    speaker: Ally Quinn
    line: You can create complex branching narratives with choices, conditions, and
      flags. The system tracks what the player has seen.
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
